when r & b was something special with the founding father of r & b groups new edition doing the solo thing in the early nineties and boyz ii men still a year or so away , troop was the premire r & b group of 1990 . the songs spread my wings , all i do is think of you and i will always love are some of the best songs to come out of early 90 's r & b and the boys earned their spot in r & b in my opinion